text:
By 2030, 30 % of all new vehicles sold in Pakistan in various categories will be Electric Vehicles (EVs). 
30% shift to electric passenger vehicles and 50% shift to electric two/three wheelers and buses by 2030;
90% shift to electric passenger vehicles and 90% shift to electric two/three wheelers and buses by 2040

